@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@token =
@tenantId =

### 获取 CSRF Token（执行写接口前先调用）
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

###

### 获取我的抄送记录（全部）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/approval/copy-records/my-copies?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 获取我的抄送记录（仅未读）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/approval/copy-records/my-copies?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&isRead=false
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 获取我的抄送记录（仅已读）
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/approval/copy-records/my-copies?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10&isRead=true
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

### 标记抄送记录为已读
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/approval/copy-records/{copyRecordId}/mark-read
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenantId}}

